snippet.title: Astro Escape: Trailer - Free Android Mobile Game on Play Store
snippet.description:
Please watch: "How to join an empty public session in GTA Online! Working after patch 1.40! 14/07/2017" 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TiYqKUETx3A
-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-

This is a trailer for my first ever game called Astro Escape which is now available on the google play store!

Free:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dsgmstudio.astroescape&hl=en_GB

Paid:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dsgmstudio.astroescapepro&hl=en_GB
